verbose_text: SA-PEG-DXM / DXM micelles could significantly reduce the percentage of TUNEL positive cells in comparison to free DXM and PEG-DXM / DXM micelles treatment at day 7 (both p < 0.05, Figure XREF_FIG B), which suggests a better anti-apoptotic effect in vivo benefiting from more DXM accumulated in the renal tissues with SA-PEG-DXM / DXM micelles.
evidence: DXM micelles could significantly reduce the percentage of TUNEL
